prompts.prompt: Create a fashion e-commerce app that has three main features. The first feature is an AI digital stylist, that knows your style and recommends you clothes accordingly. This includes a search feature. You would go through the recommended clothes by swiping like on Tinder. The second feature is a social feed where users and brands can post images and outfits they created that are directly shoppable. The third feature is your closet digitally replicated.
